Crypsense Academy is a Learn Play Earn Platform (LPEP) We specialize in aggregating blockchain knowledge, resources, and opportunities. Our Memberships give Students, Teachers, & Content Creators access to the Crypsense Academy Portal. This is a place where members can learn everything there is to know about cryptocurrency, digital assets, & blockchain technology directly from industry-leading professionals. Crypsense Academy Content is designed to teach practical monetization skills quickly. Members can play games, learn lessons, and earn rewards to pay for and monetize their education. Our goal is to provide the tools and resources needed to gain financial literacy and success in a competitive blockchain economy.

Crypsense Academy
